## Chat-D1 GateCard & SecretaryMessage 组件
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 已实现
**模块：** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/components/`
**标签：** stack:frontend
**依赖：** UiSystem-A1, Chat-A1

```typescript
// GateCard.vue
interface GateCardProps {
  gate: PendingGate
  mode: 'inline' | 'secretary'
}

// SecretaryMessage.vue
interface SecretaryMessageProps {
  gate: PendingGate
  queuePosition?: number
}
```

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Proposed
    Proposed --> Approved : boss clicks Approve
    Proposed --> Rejected : boss clicks Reject
    Proposed --> Snoozed : boss clicks Snooze
    Proposed --> Reviewing : boss clicks Review →
    Reviewing --> Proposed : drawer closed
    Snoozed --> Proposed : timer expires
    Approved --> Resolved : auto-collapse 3s
    Rejected --> Resolved : advisor reworks
    Resolved --> [*]
```

| 字段 | 类型 | 描述 |
|---|---|---|
| `gate.id` | `string` | session_id 或 run_id |
| `gate.type` | `'session' \| 'run'` | 源 composable |
| `gate.gateType` | `'goal' \| 'spec' \| 'review'` | 审批类型 |
| `gate.profession` | `string` | 等待者 |
| `gate.since` | `number` | 时间戳 |

## Chat-D5 ThinkingBlock 推理过程展示组件
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 已实现
**模块：** `frontend/src/views/ChatsView.vue`, `frontend/src/composables/useForge.ts`
**标签：** stack:frontend
**依赖：** Chat-A3

```typescript
// 新增 ForgeMessage 字段
interface ForgeMessage {
  id: string
  role: 'user' | 'assistant' | 'system' | 'tool'
  content: string
  thinking?: string        // ← 新增：推理过程内容
  timestamp: number
  tool_calls?: ToolCallInfo[]
  profession_id?: string
}
```

```typescript
// 新增 ForgeStreamEvent 变体
interface ForgeStreamEvent {
  type: 'turn_start' | 'delta' | 'thinking' | 'tool_call' | 'tool_result' | ...
  text?: string
  thinking?: string        // ← 新增
  // ... 其他字段
}
```

### 渲染行为

- **默认折叠**：以 `<details>` 元素呈现，summary 显示 💭 思考中 + 脉冲动画（仅流式传输期间）
- **点击展开**：显示 `<pre>` 包裹的完整推理内容
- **流式累积**：SSE `thinking` 事件逐块追加到 `msg.thinking`
- **历史恢复**：`loadHistory()` 从后端恢复时保留 `thinking` 字段

### 视觉样式

```css
.thinking-block details {
  border: 1px solid hsl(var(--muted-foreground) / 0.12);
  border-radius: 6px;
  background: hsl(var(--muted-foreground) / 0.03);
}
.thinking-block summary {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.3rem;
  padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.83rem;
  color: var(--af-muted);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.thinking-pulse {
  animation: thinkingPulse 1.5s infinite;
}
.thinking-content {
  padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  white-space: pre-wrap;
  word-break: break-word;
  max-height: 400px;
  overflow-y: auto;
}
```

### 数据来源

Claude Provider 的 `ContentBlockDelta::ThinkingDelta` → `ToolChatEvent::ThinkingDelta` → `ForgeStreamEvent::Thinking` → 前端 SSE `data.type === 'thinking'`

| 层级 | 事件类型 | 处理 |
|---|---|---|
| Provider | `ContentBlockDelta::ThinkingDelta` | 解析为 `ToolChatEvent::ThinkingDelta` |
| Forge | `ForgeStreamEvent::Thinking { thinking }` | 通过 SSE 发送到前端 |
| 前端 Composable | `data.type === 'thinking'` | 追加到当前 assistant 消息的 `thinking` |
| 前端视图 | `<details>` 折叠块 | 默认折叠，点击展开查看完整推理 |

